OL,3,CParaguay's Miguel Almiron gets first
OL,4,CWorld Cup red card for new Fifa rule
OL,6,FParaguay midfielder Miguel Almiron has
OL,7,Fbecome the first player to be issued a
OL,8,Fred card at the World Cup for covering
OL,9,Fhis mouth, under a new rule from Fifa.
OL,11,FThe infraction came during first-half
OL,12,Fstoppage time as Paraguay played
OL,13,FTurkey, with Almiron and defender Mert
OL,14,FMulder exchanging words on the pitch
OL,15,Ffollowing a foul.
OL,17,FAlmiron covered his mouth while saying
OL,18,Fsomething to Mulder, who immediately
OL,19,Fappealed to referee Ivan Barton for
OL,20,Fpunishment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
