OL,3,CParaguay's Miguel Almiron gets first
OL,4,CWorld Cup red card for new Fifa rule
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA new law passed by the International
OL,12,FFootball Association Board (IFAB) in
OL,13,FApril states that "any player covering
OL,14,Ftheir mouth in a confrontational
OL,15,Fsituation with an opponent may be
OL,16,Fsanctioned with a red card".
OL,18,FBarton reviewed the video and quickly
OL,19,Fruled that Almiron should be sent off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
