PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782040759
OL,3,CParaguay's Miguel Almiron gets first
OL,4,CWorld Cup red card for new Fifa rule
OL,6,FFifa president Gianni Infantino pushed
OL,7,Ffor the new rule after Benfica's
OL,8,FGianluca Prestianni tried to hide
OL,9,Fverbal insults towards Real Madrid's
OL,10,FVinicius Junior in a Champions League
OL,11,Fgame earlier this year.
OL,13,FThe IFAB said it was approving the
OL,14,Frule in a bid to address
OL,15,Fdiscriminatory and inappropriate
OL,16,Fbehaviour in football.
OL,18,FParaguay were leading 1-0 at the time,
OL,19,Fand managed to hold on for the win
OL,20,Fdespite playing a man down for the
OL,21,Fentire second half.
