PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782040759
OL,3,CParaguay's Miguel Almiron gets first
OL,4,CWorld Cup red card for new Fifa rule
OL,6,FAfter the game, Paraguay coach Gustavo
OL,7,FAlfaro said Almiron had apologised to
OL,8,Fhis team for his mistake and told him
OL,9,Fhis absence brought out the "fighting
OL,10,Fspirit" of the team.
OL,12,FThe red card means Almiron will miss
OL,13,Fthe side's final group stage match
OL,14,Fagainst Australia with second place in
OL,15,FGroup D on the line.
OL,17,F"He knew about the situation he had
OL,18,Fleft his teammates in with his
OL,19,Factions. It happened and it happened,"
OL,20,FAlfaro said.
OL,26,@qD@]OUrD@GO]
