PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782040759
OL,3,CParaguay's Miguel Almiron gets first
OL,4,CWorld Cup red card for new Fifa rule
OL,6,FThis is the second time in two games
OL,7,Fat the World Cup that Almiron has been
OL,8,Fcarded under a new rule in place this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FHe got a yellow card in the side's
OL,12,Fopening match against the United
OL,13,FStates after video review overturned a
OL,14,Fyellow card issued to Tim Ream and
OL,15,Fgave it to Almiron instead for diving.
OL,17,FThis year's World Cup has also already
OL,18,Fseen more red cards than in the two
OL,19,Ftournaments previous, with six given
OL,20,Fto players so far - and Qatar
OL,21,Freceiving two in the same game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
